Interconnected network of computers around the world is called internet.

It encompasses two things- clients and servers.
Server is a device which is online 24/7 and give data back to client when requested.

every device has unique ipo address through which it is trackable on internet.

Working of Internet-
1.client request data
2. Goes to ISP like airtel
3. Searches in Domain Name System (DNS) which stores the IP address of all Domain
4. then it goes to Internet Server Provider which gives the IP addres back to client
5. Through ip address then client can directly connect to server
